  "text": "Inspired by the CVAE-GAN [CITATION_1] , we adopt a new asymmetric loss function. More specifically, we adopt a crossentropy loss when training the discriminative network D, and the classification network C, and use a pairwise feature matching loss when updating the generative network G. This does a better job of preserving the identity while stabilizing the training process.",
